[I] GTK frontend for VIPS, an image processing library/suite

[T] nip4 is a spreadsheet-like interface to the libvips image processing
[T] library. You create a set of formula connecting your objects together, and
[T] on a change nip4 will recalculate.

[U] https://github.com/jcupitt/nip4

